This sample makes a predictive call from the split 8917 to 
an outside line number 14770539 with "Hello!" as the UserData. 
An attempt is made to connect to an agent logged in to 8917 
when a connected state was determined at the called device (14770539). 

//C# Sample:

//Creates an instance of the split device.
CSTADeviceID _CallerDevice = new CSTADeviceID ("8917", enDeviceIDType.dialingNumber );

//Creates an instance of the called device.
CSTADeviceID _CalledDevice = new CSTADeviceID ("14770539", enDeviceIDType.dialingNumber );

//Makes a call.
asxmlClient1.CSTAMakePredictiveCall ( _CallerDevice , _CalledDevice , enSignallingCondition.callEstablished , enSignallingConditionsAction .remainConnected , null , enDetectionAction.clearCalledConnection ,  "Hello!");

'VB Sample:

